@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App, VFS
statfs 核心流程（super_operations）
1. 通过路径找到对应文件系统super_block
2. 调用 s_op->statfs() 获取磁盘全局信息
3. 从超级块/位图读取：总块、空闲块、块大小
4. 拷贝结果到用户态
end note

box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space】" #LightCyan
participant "VFS 虚拟文件系统" as VFS
participant "super_block" as SB
participant "inode & dentry" as Inode
end box

App -> VFS: <color:red>①</color> statfs("/mnt", &buf)
activate VFS

VFS -> Inode: <color:red>②</color> 路径解析，获取目标inode
activate Inode
Inode --> VFS: 拿到对应文件系统的super_block
deactivate Inode

VFS -> SB: <color:red>③</color> 调用 sb->s_op->statfs()
activate SB
SB -> SB: <color:red>④</color> 读取超级块信息
note right: 总块数、空闲块、文件数、块大小
SB --> VFS: 填充统计信息
deactivate SB

VFS -> App: <color:red>⑤</color> 拷贝数据到用户态buf
VFS --> App: <color:red>⑥</color> 返回成功
deactivate VFS
@enduml